# Auto Buy/Sell System Walkthrough

I have successfully built the automated trading bot that scrapes `intradayscreener.com` for sector performance and executes trades using **Angel One SmartAPI**.

## Features
- **Smart Scraper**: Fetches real-time sector performance and stock lists from IntradayScreener API (re-engineered to work without login tokens).
- **Angel One Integration**: Uses your SmartAPI credentials to fetch 15-minute historical candle data.
- **Advanced Technicals**: Calculates **EMA 20** and **VWAP** (Intraday) using a robust Pandas implementation.
- **Smart Logic**:
    - Identifies Top Positive Sectors.
    - Filters stocks where `Price > VWAP` AND `Price > EMA 20`.
- **Dry Run Mode**: Currently set to `DRY_RUN = True` to safely log potential trades without risking capital.

