## How to Run
1.  Open your terminal.
2.  Run the bot:
    ```bash
    python main.py
    ```
3.  Check [trading_bot.log](file:///C:/Users/Ashbin/.gemini/antigravity/brain/2df2ed12-f98d-4c89-bf98-dea5fc2acbc3/trading_bot.log) inside the directory to see the signals.

## Going Live
To enable real trading:
1.  Open [main.py](file:///C:/Users/Ashbin/.gemini/antigravity/brain/2df2ed12-f98d-4c89-bf98-dea5fc2acbc3/main.py).
